      <section class="about-section">
        <div class="about-container">
          <div class="about-content">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>
              Apna Krishi was founded in 2018 with a simple mission: to bridge
              the gap between farmers and modern agricultural technology. What
              started as a small initiative to provide market prices to farmers
              in Punjab has now grown into a nationwide platform serving over
              500,000 farmers across India.
            </p>
            <p>
              We believe that every farmer deserves access to accurate
              information, fair market prices, and modern farming techniques
              regardless of their location or scale of operation.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-image">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585011650347-c59dbef5a823?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80"
